]] || colspan=2| || [[2012 Supercupa Rom\u00e2niei|Supercup]] || style=\"background:silver;\"| F || {{flagicon|Greece}} [[Pantelis Kapetanos]] || 12 ||\n|-\n| rowspan=2| '''[[2012\u201313 Liga I|2012\u201313]]''' ||  rowspan=2| 9th || rowspan=2| 34 || rowspan=2| 12 || rowspan=2| 13 || rowspan=2| 9 || rowspan=2| 56 || rowspan=2| 39 || rowspan=2| '''49''' || rowspan=2 style=\"background:silver;\"| [[2012\u201313 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|F]] || [[2012\u201313 UEFA Champions League|UCL]] || style=\"background:#ccccff;\"| GS || rowspan=2 colspan=2| || rowspan=2| {{flagicon|POR}} [[Rui Pedro Couto Ramalho|Rui Pedro]] || rowspan=2| 7 || rowspan=2|\n|-\n| [[2012\u201313 UEFA Europa League|UEL]] || R32\n|-\n| '''[[2013\u201314 Liga I|2013\u201314]]''' ||  5th || 34 || 13 || 12 ||  9 || 44 || 33 || '''51''' || [[2013\u201314 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|R32]] || colspan=2| || colspan=2| || {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Ciprian Deac]] <br /> {{flagicon|Nigeria}} [[Derick Ogbu]] || 6 ||\n|-\n| '''[[2014\u201315 Liga I|2014\u201315]]''' || style=\"background:brown;\" | 3rd || 34 || 16 ||  9 ||  9 || 49 || 29 || '''57''' || style=\"background:brown;\"| [[2014\u201315 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|SF]] || [[2014\u201315 UEFA Europa League|UEL]] || 3R || [[2014\u201315 Cupa Ligii|League Cup]] || R16 || style=\"background:gold;\"| {{flagicon|FRA}} ''' [[Gr\u00e9gory Tad\u00e9]] ''' || style=\"background:gold;\"| '''18''' ||\n|-\n| rowspan=2| ''' [[2015\u201316 Liga I|2015\u201316]] ''' || rowspan=2| 10th || 26 || 9 || 10 ||  7 || 31 || 25 || '''27'''<ref>Deducted ten points for failing to comply with licensing requirements.</ref> || rowspan=2 style=\"background:gold;\"| '''[[2015\u201316 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|W]]''' || rowspan=2 colspan=2| || [[2015\u201316 Cupa Ligii|League Cup]] || QF || rowspan=2| {{flagicon|ESP}} [[Cristian L\u00f3pez]] || rowspan=2| 13 || rowspan=2|\n|-\n| 14 || 6 || 4 || 4 || 25 || 13 || '''36'''<ref>Points halved after the regular season. Entered the play-out with 14 points.</ref> || [[2016 Supercupa Rom\u00e2niei|Supercup]] || style=\"background:silver;\"| F\n|-\n| rowspan=2| '''[[2016\u201317 Liga I|2016\u201317]]''' || rowspan=2| 4th || 26 || 14 || 7 || 5 || 42 || 23 || '''43<ref>Deducted six points for failing to comply with licensing requirements.</ref>''' || rowspan=2| [[2016\u201317 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|QF]] || rowspan=2 colspan=2| || rowspan=2| [[2016\u201317 Cupa Ligii|League Cup]] || rowspan=2| QF || rowspan=2| {{flagicon|ROM}} [[Cristian Bud]] || rowspan=2| 11 || rowspan=2|\n|-\n| 10 || 3 || 2 || 5 || 8 || 14 || ''' 33<ref>Points halved after the regular season. Entered the play-off with 22 points.</ref>'''\n|-\n| rowspan=2| '''[[2017\u201318 Liga I|2017\u201318]]''' || rowspan=2 style=\"background:gold;\"| '''1st''' || 26 || 18 || 5 || 3 || 42 || 13 || '''59''' || rowspan=2| [[2017\u201318 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|R32]] || rowspan=2 colspan=2| || rowspan=2| [[2018 Supercupa Rom\u00e2niei|Supercup]] || rowspan=2 style=\"background:gold;\"| '''W'''  || rowspan=2| {{flagicon|ARG}} [[Emmanuel Culio]] || rowspan=2| 8 || rowspan=2|\n|-\n| 10 || 5 || 5 || 0 || 12 || 6 || '''50<ref>Points halved after the regular season. Entered the play-off with 30 points.</ref>'''\n|-\n| rowspan=2| '''[[2018\u201319 Liga I|2018\u201319]]''' || rowspan=2 style=\"background:gold;\"| '''1st''' || 26 || 15 || 9 || 2 || 39 || 16 || '''54''' || rowspan=2 style=\"background:brown;\"| [[2018\u201319 Cupa Rom\u00e2niei|SF]] || [[2018\u201319 UEFA Champions League|UCL]] || style=\"background:#ccccff;\"|2R || rowspan=2|  || rowspan=2|  || rowspan=2 style=\"background:gold;\"|  {{flagicon|ROU}} '''[[George \u021aucudean]]''' || rowspan=2 style=\"background:gold;\"| '''18''' || rowspan=2|\n|-\n| 10 || 7 || 2 || 1 || 15 || 4 || '''50<ref>Points halved after the regular season. Entered the play-off with 27 points.</ref>''' || [[2018\u201319 UEFA Europa League|UEL]] || PO\n|-\n|}\n\n==Notable former players==\nThe footballers enlisted below have had international cap(s) for their respective countries at junior and/or senior level. Players whose name is listed in '''bold''' represented their countries at junior and/or senior level on through the time's passing. Additionally, these players have also had a significant number of caps and goals accumulated throughout a certain number of seasons for the club itself as well.\n\n{{For|a list of all former and current CFR Cluj players with a Wikipedia article|Category:CFR Cluj players}}\n{{Col-begin}}\n{{Col-4}}\n;Romania\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Mihai Adam]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Vasile Alexandru]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Adrian Anca]] \n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[\u0218tefan Balint]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Cristian Bud]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Sergiu Bu\u0219]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Sever Coracu]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Cristian Coroian]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Florin Costea]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Florin Dan]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Nicolae Dic\u0103]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Cristian Dulca]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Cristian Fedor]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Anton Fernbach-Ferenczi]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Ioan Hora]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Octavian Ionescu (footballer, born 1949)|Octavian Ionescu]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Vasile Jula]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[\u0218tefan Kov\u00e1cs]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Ionu\u021b Larie]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Bogdan Mara]]''' \n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Alin Minteuan]]\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Dorinel Munteanu]]''' \n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Gabriel Mure\u0219an]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Viorel Nicoar\u0103]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} [[Sorin Oncic\u0103]]\n{{Col-4}}\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Cristian Panin]]''' \n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Emil Petru]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Ionu\u021b Rada (footballer, born 1982)|Ionu\u021b Rada]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[Gheorghe R\u0103\u0219inaru]]'''\n* {{flagicon|Romania}} '''[[L\u00e1szl\u00f3 