=ROU|pos=DF|name=Rare\u0219 Ispas|other=to [[CSM Re\u0219i\u021ba]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014 |nat=ROU|pos=DF|name=[[R\u0103zvan Horj]]|other=to [[FC Universitatea Cluj|Universitatea Cluj]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014 |nat=ROU|pos=DF|name=[[Andrei Radu (footballer, born 1996)|Andrei Radu]]|other=to [[FC Politehnica Ia\u0219i (2010)|Politehnica Ia\u0219i]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014 |nat=GRE|pos=DF|name=[[Giannis Kontoes]]|other=to [[FC Academica Clinceni|Academica Clinceni]]}}\n{{Fs player|no=\u2014 |nat=ROU|pos=MF|name=[[Sebastian Mailat]]|other=to [[FC Universitatea Cluj|Universitatea Cluj]]}}\n{{Fs end}}\n\n==Club officials==\n{{col-begin}}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Board of directors===\n{| class=\"toccolours\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#94283f;color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #231f20;\" |Role\n! style=\"background:#94283f;color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #231f20;\" |Name\n|-\n| Owner\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Nelu\u021bu Varga  \n|-\n| President\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Marian B\u0103g\u0103cean\n|-\n| Sporting director\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} [[Bogdan Mara]] \n|-\n| Economic director\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Simona Baciu\n|-\n| Marketing director\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Tudor Pop\n|-\n| Team manager\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} [[Cristian Panin]]\n|-\n| General secretary\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Ioan Iva\u0219cu\n|-\n| Sporting secretary\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Iustin Balaj\n|-\n| Responsible for order and safety\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Augustin Goga\n|}\n* <small>Last updated: 15 March 2020</small>\n* <small>Source:<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cfr1907.ro/conducerea-clubului/|title=CFR 1907 &#124; Conducerea clubului}}</ref></small>\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Current technical staff===\n{| class=\"toccolours\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#94283f;color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #231f20;\" |Role\n! style=\"background:#94283f;color:#ffffff;border:1px solid #231f20;\" |Name\n|-\n| Manager\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} [[Dan Petrescu]]\n|-\n| Assistant managers\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} [[Alin Minteuan]] <br /> {{Flagicon|ROU}} [[Valeriu Bordeanu]]\n|-\n| Goalkeeping coach\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Cristian Moldovan\n|-\n| Fitness coach\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Cristian Dragot\u0103\n|-\n| Club doctor\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Cosmin Traian\n|-\n| Kinetotherapist\n| {{Flagicon|ROU}} Viorel Boncoi\n|-\n| Masseurs\n| {{Flagicon|ROM}} Iosif Mure\u0219an <br /> {{Flagicon|ROU}} Bogdan Rus\n|}\n* <small>Last updated: 15 March 2020</small>\n* <small>Source:<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://cfr1907.ro/echipa-principala/|title=CFR 1907 &#124; CFR 1907 CLUJ}}</ref></small>\n{{col-end}}\n\n==Records and statistics==\n\n===European cups all-time statistics===\n{{main|CFR Cluj in European football}}\n\n<small>''Including away match with Sevilla''</small>\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align: center;\"\n|-\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| Competition\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| {{Tooltip|S| Seasons}}\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| {{Tooltip|P| Played}}\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| {{Tooltip|W| Won}}\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| {{Tooltip|D| Drawn}}\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| {{Tooltip|L| Lost}}\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| {{Tooltip|GF| Goals for}}\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| {{Tooltip|GA| Goals against}}\n! style=\"background:#DCDCDC\"| {{Tooltip|GD| Goal difference}}\n|-\n| align=left| [[UEFA Champions League|European Cup]] / [[UEFA Champions League]]\n| 5 || 32 || 13 || 6 || 13 || 35 || 40 || \u22125\n|-\n| align=left| [[UEFA Europa League|UEFA Cup]] / [[UEFA Europa League]]\n| 6 || 26 || 9 || 5 || 12|| 23|| 31 || \u22128\n|-\n| align=left| [[UEFA Intertoto Cup]]\n| 1 || 10 || 5 || 3 || 2 || 20 || 13 || +7\n|-\n|-class=\"sortbottom\"\n! Total || 12 || 68 || 27 || 14 ||27 || 71|| 84 || \u22126\n|}\n\n===Records===\n* '''Biggest victory:''' '''CFR Cluj'''&nbsp;\u2013 Minaur Zlatna 10\u20130 (4 October 2003)\n* '''Biggest defeat:''' [[FC Rapid Bucure\u0219ti|CFR Bucure\u0219ti]]&nbsp;\u2013 '''CFR Cluj''' 12\u20132 (20 April 1949)\n* '''Player with most caps in Liga I:'''  {{Flagicon|Portugal}} [[Camora (footballer)|