|6}}.\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|20em}}\n\n{{shipevents|1941}}\n{{WWII shipwrecks}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of shipwrecks by year|1941-04]]\n[[Category:Maritime incidents in April 1941| ]]\n", "name_user": "October1944", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200e23 April:Crew fate of Kerkyra", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_shipwrecks_in_April_1941"}
